Tags:
  - Beauty-Peace=The Surface Of The Waters=The Spirit Upon the Waters
  - 317
By: Plutarch
---
They (the Egyptians) do not believe that the sun rises as a new-born babe
(Horus) from the lotus, but they portray the rising of the sun in this manner
to show darkly that his birth is a kindling from the waters.
